      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Jewelry retailers, luxury watch dealers, and online jewelry brands across Malaysia understand that safe packaging is essential for customer satisfaction and business reputation. Delicate necklaces, bracelets, rings, and precious watches require specialized protection during shipping. Bubble wrap provides proven, cost-effective cushioning that protects valuable items while maintaining professional presentation.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Why Bubble Wrap is Ideal for Jewelry Shipping</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Superior Impact & Vibration Protection</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Bubble wrap's air-filled cells absorb impact energy, protecting delicate gemstones, watch movements, and intricate metalwork from damage. Each bubble acts as a shock absorber during courier transport across KL, Cheras, Kajang, and Peninsular Malaysia.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Lightweight Packaging Reduces Shipping Costs</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Unlike heavy wooden boxes or rigid cases, bubble wrap adds minimal weight to jewelry shipments. This reduces dimensional weight charges and improves profit margins for online jewelry retailers selling across Malaysia.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Moisture & Humidity Control</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Sealed bubble wrap protects jewelry from Malaysia's high humidity. Moisture control is especially important for watches, pearls, and gemstones susceptible to corrosion and tarnishing during tropical storage and transport.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Professional Appearance & Unboxing Experience</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Carefully bubble-wrapped jewelry creates premium unboxing experiences that delight customers and encourage positive reviews and social sharing. This enhances brand perception for luxury jewelry brands in Malaysia.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Best Practices for Jewelry Bubble Wrap Protection</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Individual Item Wrapping</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Wrap each piece of jewelry separately in acid-free tissue first, then layer with bubble wrap. This prevents pieces from scratching each other and allows independent movement without impact transfer between items.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Double-Wrapping Delicate Pieces</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">For high-value watches, diamond rings, or intricate necklaces, use two layers of bubble wrap with a protective barrier in between. This extra cushioning prevents damage from drops or rough handling during courier sorting and delivery.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Securing in Rigid Boxes</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Place bubble-wrapped jewelry in rigid boxes with additional padding. This prevents shifting and compression during stacking on delivery trucks. Use tamper-evident tape to indicate package integrity to customers.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Tarnish Prevention for Silver & Gold</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">For silver jewelry, use anti-tarnish tissue wrapped before bubble wrap application. This dual protection prevents oxidation and maintains jewelry appearance during long-term storage or extended delivery times across Malaysia.</p>
      </section>

