        <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Shipping Luxury Watches Across Malaysia</h2>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Premium Bubble Wrap for Timepiece Protection</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Luxury watches contain delicate movements, sapphire crystals, and precision components sensitive to impact. Use premium 1/2 inch bubble wrap with larger bubbles designed specifically for fine watches. Layer protection on sides, top, and bottom.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Humidity & Condensation Prevention</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Watches in Malaysia's tropical climate risk internal moisture. Include desiccant packets in boxes with bubble-wrapped watches. Sealed bubble wrap helps maintain stable humidity levels inside shipment boxes.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Insurance & Tracking for High-Value Shipments</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">For watches over RM 5,000, use insured courier services. Pair bubble wrap protection with professional packaging and tracking to ensure valuable timepieces reach customers or retailers safely across Peninsular Malaysia.</p>
      </section>

