            <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-3 leading-relaxed">Reusing bubble wrap risks reduced cushioning effectiveness if bubbles are popped. For valuable jewelry, fresh bubble wrap ensures premium protection and professional appearance with customers.</p>
