        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-4">Jewelry and watches deserve premium protection during shipping. Bubble wrap provides proven, affordable, professional-grade cushioning that keeps valuable items safe while maintaining brand reputation and customer satisfaction across Malaysia.</p>
